  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool</span>. This alien weapon comes with a devastating close-range <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scatter Blaster</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Paralysis Mortar</span> installed.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Take</span> this Multi-Tool to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current Multi-Tool. Swap between active Multi-Tools from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一台专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>。这把外星武器预装有能够在近距离发挥毁灭性威力的<span class=\"name name-technology\">散射爆破器</span>以及<span class=\"name name-technology\">瘫痪迫击炮</span>。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收下</span>这个多用途工具，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的多用途工具<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的工具部分切换可用的多用途工具。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組</span>。這把外星武器配備近距離的<span class=\"name name-technology\">雙管霰彈槍</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">癱瘓迫擊砲</span>，極具毀滅性。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">取走</span>這個工具組加入你的收藏，或是與目前工具組<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 的機能選項切換使用中的工具組。"
  },
